tc.research_name.CRUCIBLE=坩堝
tc.research_text.CRUCIBLE=沸騰且冒著泡
tc.research_page.CRUCIBLE.1=只需對著放置在地上的普通煉藥鍋揮舞你的法杖，你就能得到這種具有魔力的坩堝。<BR>坩堝對秘術使來說是重要的工具。它能夠讓你將常態的物品分解成其蘊含的要素並且如你所願地組合。<BR>坩堝需要放置在一個長久熱源(或是閃耀之光)的上方，並裝滿水。當水開始沸騰並冒著氣泡的時候可以向其中投入物品，這樣物品就會分解破壞成其要素源質。<BR>當坩堝中的源質符合正確的配方，
tc.research_page.CRUCIBLE.2=就可以向坩堝內投入稱為觸媒的特殊物品。觸媒將作為凝聚源質的核心，轉換成全新的物品，並從坩堝中彈出。<BR>多餘的源質會留存在坩堝中備用，但長期讓要素殘留在坩堝中不是個好主意，因為多餘的源質終將分解成咒波釋出。<BR>使用坩堝製作物品會消耗坩堝中少量的水，因此你最後還是需要重新添水。
tc.research_page.CRUCIBLE.3=你可以藉由對著坩堝使用法杖shift右鍵來清空坩堝中的源質，但這會讓坩堝中的源質全部化為咒波釋放到大氣中…… 因此你不會希望經常這麼做。<LINE>以下是所有人皆能使用的一些基礎煉金配方。
tc.research_page.CRUCIBLE.4=§n均衡碎片§r<BR><BR>向普通的魔力碎片灌注其餘五種它不具有的原初要素的魔力碎片，最終得到的就是這種六大原初要素相互平衡的，能與原初能量完美共鳴的水晶碎片。<BR> 在熔爐中冶煉平衡碎片能夠得到世界鹽(參見後文)。
tc.research_page.CRUCIBLE.5=§n世界鹽§r<BR><BR>世界鹽，世人稱之為秘術使之鹽，是加熱均衡碎片使其分解得到的細粉。<BR>正如凡俗世界的鹽一樣，秘術使之鹽也能夠給所有那些普通的魔法配方或儀式增添美妙的滋味(這是個隱喻)。它是一種強力的黏合劑。能夠讓彼此間最暌離的魔力要素聚合在一起。
#
tc.research_name.METALLURGY=秘術錠
tc.research_text.METALLURGY=魔導金屬
tc.research_page.METALLURGY.1=已經證實通過秘術學原理能夠輕易處理金屬材料。你的首次相關實驗發現了秘術錠。<BR>秘術錠是向普通的金屬材料灌注天然魔力得到的產物。相比鐵，它更堅硬，也更能容載附魔能量。<BR>這種金屬廣泛用於合成更高級的魔導設備。<BR>也可以用它使用慣常的合成方法製作出相應的工具，武器和裝備。
tc.research_page.METALLURGY.2=秘術錠固然有諸多實用特性，但有時候平凡的材料在特定用途上會更勝一籌。黃銅是一種堅固耐用，摩擦係數小的金屬材料，非常適合用來製造精密的機械設備。<BR>但由於你所處的這個宇宙之特殊波動性導致你可能無法找到足夠的黃銅。好在你找到一種煉金方法能製作出這種有用的金屬。
#
tc.research_name.NITOR=閃耀之光
tc.research_text.NITOR=永恆的花火
tc.research_page.NITOR.1=這團發光的花火靠魔力來燃燒自己。這種不滅的永恆之光所生成的熱能遠少於其光芒，但是它們足夠依舊是個穩定的能量來源。<BR>閃耀之光也能安置在世界中作為魔法光源，你可以在工作台中為它染色。
#
tc.research_name.ALUMENTUM=源動之焰
tc.research_text.ALUMENTUM=神秘的能量團
tc.research_page.ALUMENTUM.1=一團伴隨著跳動火焰的物質，輕微的顛簸便可能導致一次劇烈的能量釋放。這種不穩定的能源可能能成為很高效的燃料。<BR>如果你不是特別喜歡爆炸的話就別把它隨便丟出去。
#
tc.research_name.PHIAL=玻璃管型瓶
tc.research_text.PHIAL=秘術容器
tc.research_page.PHIAL.1=玻璃管型瓶能夠盛放各種形式的液體或者其他物質，但對秘術使而言最為重要的是它容納要素源質的能力。
#
tc.research_name.BOTTLETAINT=污染瓶
tc.research_text.BOTTLETAINT=你要這東西做什麼？
tc.research_page.BOTTLETAINT.1=清除污染是一回事，但有沒有考慮要擴散它呢？<BR>只需濃縮污染要素並收集在瓶子裡，並將它扔在你希望創造污染的地方，一切就完成了。但是你究竟是為了什麼？
#
tc.research_name.TAINTSHARD=Taint Shard 
tc.research_text.TAINTSHARD=Corrupting shards
tc.research_page.TAINTSHARD.1=Tainted vis shards are usually (and fortunately) quite hard to come by. Still, they have their uses and you have found a way to create them via alchemy.<BR>The process is not particularly efficient as the amount of vitium required to everwhelm a healthy vis shard is much greater than the resulting tainted shard actually contains.  
#
tc.research_name.ALCHEMICALDUPLICATION=煉金複製
tc.research_text.ALCHEMICALDUPLICATION=好東西不可能擁有太多
tc.research_page.ALCHEMICALDUPLICATION.1=在自然界中有許多的物質可以用於煉金術。<BR>透過謹慎且小心地加入正確要素，你能把它們變得更多。
#
tc.research_name.ALCHEMICALMANUFACTURE=煉金製造
tc.research_text.ALCHEMICALMANUFACTURE=條條大路通羅馬
tc.research_page.ALCHEMICALMANUFACTURE.1=你掌握了煉金術的基礎，準備好用基礎材料來製造更複雜的物質。<BR>你寫下了幾個配方能讓你用煉金術獲得平常取得不易的物質。
#
tc.research_name.ENTROPICPROCESSING=混沌製程
tc.research_text.ENTROPICPROCESSING=讓事情變得更糟？
tc.research_page.ENTROPICPROCESSING.1=創造普通物質與魔法物質相當令人滿足，但有時你只是想把物體打碎，以獲得更基本的物質。有什麼方法比增加熵能更簡單？<BR>但是事實上，在某方面而言這並不是一個好方法，但是要追求進步不就是會有風險嗎？
#
tc.research_name.PUREMETAL=金屬晶簇化
tc.research_text.PUREMETAL=將金屬礦結晶成礦物晶簇
tc.research_page.PUREMETAL.1=礦物晶簇是稀有而純淨的金屬聚合體。你發現一種方法能提純並聚合礦物得到礦晶簇。<BR>冶煉這些礦晶簇比起普通礦石能得到雙倍的金屬錠。
#
tc.research_name.TRANSMETAL=嬗變術
tc.research_text.TRANSMETAL=金屬變換
tc.research_page.TRANSMETAL.1=你發現透過將金屬粒浸泡在§5metallum§0與其他源質中可使它增量。
#
tc.research_name.TALLOW=魔導肉脂
tc.research_text.TALLOW=以魔力熬製脂肪
tc.research_page.TALLOW.1=將肉塊投入坩堝中熬煉，製作出具有多種奧術用途的魔導肉脂。<BR>這種肉脂可以用作製作肉脂蠟燭。可以在工作台中可以使用顏料為蠟燭染色。
#
tc.research_name.DISTILESSENTIA=源質蒸餾
tc.research_text.DISTILESSENTIA=收穫源質
tc.research_page.DISTILESSENTIA.1=你未來會需求使用龐大種類的數種要素-而非存在法杖內的寥寥幾種原初要素。<BR>利用基本煉金原理你已瞭解了如何分解物品將其轉化為基本的要素源質。<BR>首先你需要一台§l源質熔煉爐§r。源質熔煉爐就像普通熔爐那樣燃燒燃料獲得熱量，但並不用於煉製礦物，而是用以分解物品得到要素源質黏漿。這項程序並非完美，大約會有20%的源質會轉化為咒波而流失。
tc.research_page.DISTILESSENTIA.2=這項製程的下一步是提取源質黏漿並以§l奧術蒸餾器§r進行蒸餾。<BR>為了達成這項目的，你必須將奧術蒸餾器安裝在熔煉爐上方。複數的蒸餾器可以安置在彼此的上方以增加儲存量，但這麼做並不能影響熔煉的速度。源質黏漿會逐漸流入蒸餾器並依個別要素分離開來。<BR>當熔煉爐使用源動之焰最為燃料時，蒸餾速度會有顯著的提升。
tc.research_page.DISTILESSENTIA.3=要素源質能以管型瓶、封罐以及其他更複雜的裝置提取。
tc.research_page.DISTILESSENTIA.4=§n奧術風箱§r<BR>將奧術風箱安放在冶煉爐旁將能提高產熱效率，提升分解物件的速度。
#
tc.research_name.DISTILESSENTIA2=秘術源質熔煉爐
tc.research_text.DISTILESSENTIA2=收穫源質
tc.research_page.DISTILESSENTIA2.1=秘術熔煉爐工作方式如同普通的熔煉爐，但其效率高達85%而非80%。<BR>最主要優勢在於分解黏漿的速度為普通熔煉爐的兩倍。
#
tc.research_name.DISTILESSENTIA3=虛無鋼源質熔煉爐
tc.research_text.DISTILESSENTIA3=收穫源質
tc.research_page.DISTILESSENTIA3.1=虛無鋼熔煉爐工作方式類似普通的熔煉爐，但它的效率高達95%而非80%。<BR>它分解黏漿的速度會比普通熔煉爐稍快，但不及秘術熔煉爐。
#
tc.research_name.IMPROVED_DISTILLATION=源質蒸餾改良
tc.research_text.IMPROVED_DISTILLATION=源質收穫…改良
tc.research_page.IMPROVED_DISTILLATION.1=熔煉爐的加工速度非常快，但它還能變得更快，尤其是熔煉爐將源質黏漿分離成可用源質的過程還有很大的提速空間。<BR>每個附加在熔煉爐側面的附屬黏漿泵都能夠作為輔助的處理設備，向安置在它上方的蒸餾器輸出精煉好的源質。
tc.research_page.IMPROVED_DISTILLATION.2=你還研究出一種方法以控制熔煉過程中產生的咒波。讓源質黏漿流經源質濾管的附加裝置，就能夠將咒波分離出來，將它變成安全無害的蒸汽排放出來。<BR>還可以加裝第三級裝置來進一步減少咒波產量，但隨著加裝的排放口數量增多其效果會衰減。
#
tc.research_name.JARLABEL=封罐與標籤
tc.research_text.JARLABEL=儲存和整理要素源質
tc.research_page.JARLABEL.1=可以用§l封罐§r儲存要素源質。<BR>只要將封罐放置在地上，就能夠非常明瞭直觀地儲存源質。由於魔法的力量，使用或者存放封罐中的源質都是小菜一碟的事情。<BR>手持封罐直接點擊奧術蒸餾器就可以將源質裝進罐中。你也可以使用要素管型瓶來填充或清空罐子。<BR>此外它們還非常便於大量且密集地進行源質儲存。
tc.research_page.JARLABEL.2=空手狀態下按住潛行鍵(Shift)右擊封罐或者蒸餾器能夠清空它們。<BR>只要罐子裡裝有源質，你就可以貼上§l封罐標籤§r。<BR>標籤可以將罐子鎖定為接收特定類型的要素源質，而不再接收其他類型的源質。<BR>空手對著罐子貼著標籤的一面按住潛行右鍵可以取下標籤。注意如果誤點了其他面會清空罐子裡裝的源質。
tc.research_page.JARLABEL.3=你可以對著空罐子使用與某種要素綁定過的標籤(在合成台中合成裝有要素的管型瓶與標籤)，這樣空罐子會自動綁定到這種要素，變成對應標籤的封罐。而標籤上的要素僅僅只是標記，並不會消耗源質。<BR>對著裝滿了源質的罐子使用，則會把罐子變成和其容納要素相對應的標籤封罐。<LINE>綁定過某種要素的標籤只需要放入合成網格進行一次合成就能變回空白標籤。
#
tc.research_name.ETHEREALBLOOM=天域花
tc.research_text.ETHEREALBLOOM=純潔的花朵
tc.research_page.ETHEREALBLOOM.1=水銀花常常生長在銀樹附近的陰影之中，但是它亦有自己獨特的魔法屬性。<BR>就像銀樹，水銀花也潛藏著休眠中的淨化魔力。你已經找到一種方法喚醒這種魔力，並將其轉化為天域花。<BR>天域花，能夠緩慢而確實地恢復這片被神秘力量(包括我們稱之為污染的疫病)所影響、破壞的大地，使其重回昔日的榮光之下。雖然它並不能夠直接對抗污染，但很少污染植物能在天域花所處的環境中存活，進而使之逐漸凋亡。
tc.research_page.ETHEREALBLOOM.2=這種花只能淨化沐浴在其榮光之下的8格範圍內的土地。
#
tc.research_name.TUBES=要素源質管道
tc.research_text.TUBES=運輸要素源質
tc.research_page.TUBES.1=你已發現了好些運輸要素源質的方法，但都被證明難以與大規模的煉金操作相適應-現在這問題解決了。<BR>你已破解了製作穩定及相對密封的管道的關鍵所在。儘管普通的化學物質可以用玻璃管道運輸，但某些類型的要素源質卻可能溶解掉或者直接穿透玻璃。在玻璃管道上裹上鐵皮並用水銀處理，讓即使最不穩定的源質也能安全通過。黃金的管道配件裝飾得管道系統極其美觀。
tc.research_page.TUBES.2=管道可以與各種類型的奧術設備相連，儘管一般你主要用它連接封罐和蒸餾器。<BR>要素源質會主動流向任意可以容納它的容器，例如封罐。<BR>裝有不同源質的封罐只會吸引那些同類要素源質。但管道一次只能吸入並運輸一種類型的源質，吸力最高的會優先處理。若無法恰當使用閥門很容易導致管道系統堵塞，所以閥門的使用尤其關鍵。
tc.research_page.TUBES.3=當你看到氣體被從一個管道被排出，這意味著不同的吸力會干擾彼此。顏色告訴了你其吸入源質類型的線索。<LINE>要素閥門如同普通管道，但可以通過手動或者紅石信號控制其開閉。關閉閥門後通過它的源質流會被阻斷。<LINE>要素音叉是為管道系統排障的方便工具。你可以使用它查看管道或其他使用源質的設備中當前容納著何種源質以及它們的吸力強弱。
tc.research_page.TUBES.4=可以藉由魔杖點擊來斷開或接上相鄰的源質管道。<BR>也能用魔杖點擊中央部份來像調節閥門一樣旋轉它。
#
tc.research_name.CENTRIFUGE=奧術離心機
tc.research_text.CENTRIFUGE=分離物品
tc.research_page.CENTRIFUGE.1=奧術離心機是一種令人驚艷的煉金設備，能夠將源質分解為更基本的前置要素。<BR>當複合要素的源質從下方流入離心機，就會被慢慢分解成組成它們的前置的複合要素或原初要素。但每消耗一點源質只能得到一點前置要素源質。<BR>分離得到的要素源質需要從離心機頂部抽走。由於管道壓力系統的特性，最好在離心機頂部連接一個§5源質緩衝器§0。
#
tc.research_name.JARVOID=虛空封罐
tc.research_text.JARVOID=源質太多？不可能！
tc.research_page.JARVOID.1=虛空封罐用起來如同普通的封罐，但是有一個重要的不同之處：即使它們裝滿了也能夠繼續接收要素源質，但多餘的要素源質會化為咒波排出。這讓你總會有這種源質可用，而不至於糾結多做出來的那些。<BR>就如同普通的罐子，虛空罐也可以貼上標籤。但它們在源質管道系統中的優先級低於其他貼了標籤的封罐(介於未貼標籤的罐子和貼了標籤的罐子之間)。<BR>A word of warning: occasionally the venting process causes flux, but this is fortunately rare. 
#
tc.research_name.TUBEFILTER=高階源質管道
tc.research_text.TUBEFILTER=你需要什麼，要用在何處
tc.research_page.TUBEFILTER.1=§n過濾源質管道§r如同普通管道，但可以貼標籤。當使用標籤標記後它將限定只能輸送指定類型的要素源質。<BR>空手時按住shift點擊將取下標籤。
tc.research_page.TUBEFILTER.2=§n限制源質管道§r如同普通管道，但它們會將經過此管道的的吸取力減半。<LINE>§n定向源質管道§r只接受某個方向上抽取來的源質，藍色標記指示它所能被抽取的方向。
tc.research_page.TUBEFILTER.3=源質緩衝器能夠允許你暫時儲存一定量的源質，總計8點，可以是不同源質類型的任意組合。如同封罐它會自動吸收源質，但其吸力是各種可能中最小的(吸收的優先級最低)。<BR>換言之通常只有在直接將其安附在源質來源處它才能吸入源質，然而管道可以連接在它所有的方向上，這意味著除了用它來提取奧術離心機這種大容量空間的設備中的源質以外意義甚微。<BR>你可以為緩衝器安裝奧術風箱，每個風箱提升32點吸力。
tc.research_page.TUBEFILTER.4=另外你可以向普通的管道般各別的開啟或關閉緩衝器的每一面，而當你按住shift點擊其任意連接處，能將那一面的吸力抑制在1(藍)或0(紅)。這個特性使得源質緩衝器在輸送源質時有許多有趣的可能性。
#
tc.research_name.THAUMATORIUM=自動煉金
tc.research_text.THAUMATORIUM=大眾化煉金
tc.research_page.THAUMATORIUM.1=迄今為止煉金術稍微有些變成一件撞運氣的工作。誤算數量的要素，品質低劣的源質和煉金配料全都需要手動勞作去混合。這些總算成為了過去。<BR>秘術煉金塔真是了不起的發明！它使得秘術使者能夠選擇使用何種配方，添加何種觸媒。它還能夠使用管道自動從可用的源頭抽取源質。只要尚還提供有觸媒它就能夠一直完美地產出所需的物品。<BR>這種坩堝並不需要添水，但下方依然需要提供熱源。
tc.research_page.THAUMATORIUM.2=當你開啟該設備會看見一些格子。左上方的格子用來放置觸媒。添置好後便可以自右上格子的可成列表中選擇你想要的配方。<BR>下方的長條會按所需順序顯示所需的源質。當設備運作時它還會顯示出進度條。<BR>製成的物品會從設備前方彈出，或者進入到放置在彈射口位置的容器中。
tc.research_page.THAUMATORIUM.3=一般來說一個煉金塔只能同時使用一個配方，但在其周圍安附助記方陣就能增加它同時掌握的配方數量。<BR>每個助記方陣能夠增添2個配方。
#
tc.research_name.BATHSALTS=淨化浴鹽
tc.research_text.BATHSALTS=洗滌身心
tc.research_page.BATHSALTS.1=扭曲即使對最謹慎的秘術使來說都非常危險。尤其身染數種扭曲的秘術使更是不勝其擾。而淨化浴鹽有助於解決他們的問題。 <BR>只要將這些鹽分溶解在水中，就能將水變為銀光閃閃的淨化之泉，以其進行沐浴，能夠舒緩日間的疲憊，暫時祛除扭曲的現象。需要注意的是，秘術使所患扭曲愈甚，沐浴淨化之水所產生的保護效果持續時間就愈短暫。<BR>這些浴鹽難以保存，如若隨意放置極容易溶解。
#
tc.research_name.LIQUIDDEATH=化骨亡水
tc.research_text.LIQUIDDEATH=僅限外用
tc.research_page.LIQUIDDEATH.1=這種液體是極其危險之溶劑，豈止骨肉，即使更加堅硬的物體也難以承受。沒有任何生命體或相似於生命者能與之共存。<BR>除去非常顯而易見的用法外，這種邪惡的物質還擁有一種奇妙的特性：被消融的生物種蘊含的源質會以可採集的結晶的形式留存下來。<BR>至於這些結晶究竟有何妙用就有待讀者自行發揮想像力了。 
#
tc.research_name.ARCANESPA=奧術浴池
tc.research_text.ARCANESPA=時髦的休閒
tc.research_page.ARCANESPA.1=手動將浴鹽灑進水裡麻煩又無趣，好在秘術使能利用一些魔法手段輕鬆地解決這個問題。<BR>你製造出了一台方便的設備，能夠自動混合水和浴鹽，並將它們泵出到設備上方的空間。泵出的流體將填滿機器正上方5X5大小的區域。<BR>此外，你發現它也能用於將任意其他流體泵出。你可以使用自動化設備裝填，或是以容器點擊它來填充。通入紅石信號能夠將它關閉。
#
tc.research_name.SANESOAP=祛邪肥皂
tc.research_text.SANESOAP=擺脫那些骯髒的念頭吧
tc.research_page.SANESOAP.1=淨化肉體固然容易，但是若受到扭曲糾纏，也同樣需要洗滌心靈的妙法。<BR>這塊肥皂能夠洗淨肉體上的污垢，但其真正特別之處在於還能對你的精神產生效果。它能夠祛除所有暫時性的扭曲。並有小機率能夠祛除非常駐的扭曲。<BR>浸泡淨化之泉或處於扭曲防護狀態時使用這塊肥皂能夠增加生效的幾率。
#
tc.research_name.ESSENTIACRYSTAL=源質結晶器 
tc.research_text.ESSENTIACRYSTAL=要結實的貨幣，還是要流動的資產？
tc.research_page.ESSENTIACRYSTAL.1=你差不多已經掌握了如何將凝聚的物體轉換為液態的源質，所以反過來也並非多麻煩的事。<BR>源質結晶器從管道系統中抽取源質並緩慢地將其凝聚成稱為源之晶的小碎片。源之晶易於管理運輸，且非常穩定。<BR>結晶器會將凝聚的水晶彈出來或者裝入旁邊的容器，通入紅石信號可以關閉這功能。<BR>它會自動從靈氣中提取Terra魔力來運作。
#
tc.research_name.ESSENTIATRANSPORT=Essentia Transfusion
tc.research_text.ESSENTIATRANSPORT=Aerial Essentia
tc.research_page.ESSENTIATRANSPORT.1=During the infusion crafting process essentia is drawn directly from jars and floats through the air to the infusion matrix. The magic of the matrix keeps it stable enough for the infusion process, but normally the essentia is still changed in such a way that it becomes unusable for anything else. You have discovered a way to transport essentia in a similar manner without it becoming unstable.<BR>You have drawn up plans for two devices. The Filling Essentia Transfuser can take essentia directly from a pipe network or other essentia source and transport it to jars within 16 blocks of the direction it is facing.  
tc.research_page.ESSENTIATRANSPORT.2=The Emptying Essentia Transfuser does the opposite - drawing essentia from jars within range and placing it within tubes or devices requiring essentia of a specific type. 
#
#
# Golemancy 
#######################
tc.research_name.BASICGOLEMANCY=基礎傀儡學
tc.research_text.BASICGOLEMANCY=運轉控制
tc.research_page.BASICGOLEMANCY.1=你早已研究過一些非常基礎、原始，任何人都能製造但存在許多瑕疵的傀儡。它們充滿可能性，卻無法受人控制。<BR>你確定你能夠做得比這更好。
#
tc.research_name.MATSTUDWOOD=材料專題：木材
tc.research_text.MATSTUDWOOD=進階木材加工
tc.research_page.MATSTUDWOOD.1=由於傀儡學需要的精密部件不容許任何閃失，因此對你的加工技術有更高的要求。你需要同時提升自己在世俗與奧術素材方面的知識和水平。你的第一個鑽研目標是木材。<BR>木材是一種多用途的材質，儘管有些脆弱，但是輕盈且易於加工。你發現宏偉之木這種優秀的木材非常適合用於傀儡學。
#
tc.research_name.MATSTUDIRON=材料專題：鐵
tc.research_text.MATSTUDIRON=進階鐵材加工
tc.research_page.MATSTUDIRON.1=鐵擁有許多值得推薦的特性-它比木材更加結實且具備木材所沒有的延展性。然而鐵的加工難度更大且相當沉重。
#
tc.research_name.MATSTUDBRASS=材料專題：黃銅
tc.research_text.MATSTUDBRASS=進階黃銅加工
tc.research_page.MATSTUDBRASS.1=黃銅比鐵稍微柔軟，但作為精密機械元件而言依舊相當結實。在你看來簡直是傀儡學研究能找到的最佳凡俗材料，你完全想像不出還能找到更適合用來加工精緻金屬的材質。而且外觀也非常賞心悅目。
#
tc.research_name.MATSTUDTHAUMIUM=材料專題：秘術錠
tc.research_text.MATSTUDTHAUMIUM=進階秘術金屬加工
tc.research_page.MATSTUDTHAUMIUM.1=秘術錠是一種如海綿般吸滿了魔力的奧術金屬。它的強度明顯高於鐵。但不幸它比鐵稍重，而且其強度也使加工變得更加困難。<BR>因此這種材料無法像黃銅般製成精密的發條裝置，秘術金屬的強度使它適合用在那些與精密度相比更需要高強度的結構上。
#
tc.research_name.MATSTUDVOID=材料專題：虛無鋼
tc.research_text.MATSTUDVOID=進階虛無鋼加工
tc.research_page.MATSTUDVOID.1=虛無鋼相對輕盈且柔軟，正常而言不會用於機械。但其變化性以及自我修復的特點卻讓樂於跳脫思考框架秘術使想到許多種有趣的可能。
#
tc.research_name.MATSTUDCLAY=Material Studies: Clay
tc.research_text.MATSTUDCLAY=Advanced Clay crafting
tc.research_page.MATSTUDCLAY.1=Clay is not particularly strong, light or durable, but it is easy to work, highly resistant to fire and lighter than iron. Basically, the perfect choice for a thaumaturge on a budget.
#
tc.research_name.HUNGRYCHEST=饕餮之箱
tc.research_text.HUNGRYCHEST=無需等待你開啟
tc.research_page.HUNGRYCHEST.1=饕餮之箱能自動拾取接觸到它的物品。
#
tc.research_name.ARCANEBORE=奧術鑽掘機
tc.research_text.ARCANEBORE=採礦業的進化
tc.research_page.ARCANEBORE.1=你已經發現一種擁有採掘核心能力，且具有更大的工作範圍的奧術設備，不僅如此，這台機器還可以無人監控地自動運行。只需要將它安裝在特別的基座上，先以法杖將其方向調校正確後，再用紅石信號啟動即可。<BR>奧術鑽掘機需要兩件東西才能正常工作。首先你需要將採掘核心放在物品欄左側格子中，法杖核心的附魔效果也會被加成到鑽掘機上。
tc.research_page.ARCANEBORE.2=再來，你需要在右邊格子裡放置一個任意類型的鎬子。鎬的材料對鑽掘機運行效果影響很小，但其耐久直接決定鑽掘機的運轉時間。此外，就如同核心，鎬子上的附魔效果也能夠被加成到鑽掘機上。<BR>奧術鑽掘機只能安裝在奧術鑽探基座的上方或下方。挖掘到的物品都會從鑽探基座的噴嘴所朝方向彈出。<BR>若有箱子則會自動放入其物品欄。你可以用法杖改變奧術鑽掘機的方向。
tc.research_page.ARCANEBORE.3=倘若向鑽掘機供應§8Perditio§0源質將大大提升其鑽探效率。可以如平常一樣使用管道供應源質。一點§8Perditio§0源質能夠讓鑽掘機以更快的速度挖掘接下來的20個方塊。若是沒有§8Perditio§0源質供應，它將從周圍靈氣抽取能量，每單位挖掘一格。相較於直接供應源質慢了許多。
#
tc.research_name.TRAVELTRUNK=旅之篋
tc.research_text.TRAVELTRUNK=隨身行李
tc.research_page.TRAVELTRUNK.1=這是一項對所有四處奔忙的秘術使來說都非常有用的傀儡學研究衍生產品：旅之篋。<BR>這個木頭做的箱子會充滿活力，蹦蹦跳跳跟在主人身後，充當一個隨身的儲物空間，裝下你拾取的任意物品。<BR>旅之篋做得非常結實堅韌，能夠承受大量的攻擊，而且不畏火焰，也不會受到掉落傷害。<BR>旅之篋將追隨它的主人前往任何地方——甚至是跨位面的旅行，但是如果你希望它不再跟著你，在它的界面裡也有個很方便的按鈕來讓它留在原地。
tc.research_page.TRAVELTRUNK.2=旅之篋能夠隨時間緩緩回復它所受到的傷害，但你也可以餵給它任意食物來加快這個過程。<BR>用傀儡使之鈴能夠像回收傀儡那樣回收旅之篋，但這樣做會讓旅之篋裝著的所有物品掉落在地上，按住潛行點擊它會取下安裝在它身上的升級，但有一定幾率遺失。<BR>就像普通的傀儡那樣，旅之篋能安裝升級，但升級將對旅之篋起到獨特的效果。如果你已經發現了相關升級可以閱讀後面幾頁來查看詳細信息。
tc.research_page.TRAVELTRUNK.UAI=§n傀儡升級：風§r<BR>安裝該升級使旅之篋移動更加迅捷。
tc.research_page.TRAVELTRUNK.UEA=§n傀儡升級：地§r<BR>安裝該升級會為旅之篋額外增加一行物品空間來攜運更多物品。
tc.research_page.TRAVELTRUNK.UFI=§n傀儡升級：火§r<BR>安裝該升級後旅之篋會在主人遭受攻擊時挺身而出。
tc.research_page.TRAVELTRUNK.UWA=§n傀儡升級：水§r<BR>安裝該升級後旅之篋將不能被主人外的任何人開啟。<BR>並對各種毀滅性的傷害具有更高的抵禦能力。
tc.research_page.TRAVELTRUNK.UOR=§n傀儡升級：秩序§r<BR>安裝該升級後即使用用傀儡使之鈴回收，旅之篋也能保留住裝在它體內的物品。當按住潛行鍵點擊時它還會和平時一樣掉落出物品。
tc.research_page.TRAVELTRUNK.UEN=§n傀儡升級：混沌§r<BR>安裝該升級後旅之篋會自己吸取附近的掉落物品。
#
tc.research_name.MINDCLOCKWORK=發條之心
tc.research_text.MINDCLOCKWORK=賦予生命
tc.research_page.MINDCLOCKWORK.1=鐵傀儡,雪傀儡或者其他能放一塊比較的類似造物都有一個共通之處:它們的行為都不受控制,難以預測.<BR>驅使他們行動的是狂野的具有自由意志的靈魂.這正是問題所在.<BR>如果你打算製造一些智能的魔力僕人,你就得考慮賦予他們能夠接受命令的思維.最簡單的解決方案是製造出一個使用神秘學驅動的發條裝置.它只具有極其有限的自主思維,不過這才僅僅是開始而已嘛.
tc.research_page.MINDCLOCKWORK.2=Of course, now that you have a mind it is time to put it to use.<BR>You have designed a special press that will allow you to craft simple golems. It includes an anvil and forge to make assembling the parts easier.<LINE>To assemble as golem you simply access the Golem Press and select the components you wish to craft the golem from. For now your selection is fairly limited, but you are sure you will develop more.
tc.research_page.MINDCLOCKWORK.3=Each golem is made up from up to 5 components: The base material, a type of head, arms, legs and an optional addon module. Simply select which of these you want to use and a list of crafting components will be displayed on the right. You need to have the listed components in your inventory before you can start the crafting process.<BR>Listed in the middle of the interface you will see the traits, hearts, armor and damage the golem will possess.<BR>Lastly you will need to supply Machina essentia to the press. Several ports are provided below the main press mechanism for this purpose.
tc.research_page.MINDCLOCKWORK.4=You can now place the golem wherever you wish, but it will not do much unless you also place down a §5Golem Control Seal§0. To learn more about them see the reseach category that will have unlocked.<BR>When they have no tasks to perform, golems will return to the spot they were originally placed. You can pick up a golem by right clicking on it with a wand.
#
tc.research_name.GOLEMDIRECT=Golem Mastery
tc.research_text.GOLEMDIRECT=Taking a direct hand in things
tc.research_page.GOLEMDIRECT.1=Having golems mindlessly following seals is not your only goal. You want them to mindlessly follow you as well.<BR>You can now right click on a golem with the §5Golemancer's Bell§0 to have it follow you. While following you it will no longer obey seals and combat capable golems will defend you in combat.<BR>Clicking on the golem again will once again return it to normal functioning and its home location will be set to its current location. 
#
tc.research_name.CONTROLSEALS=Golem Control Seals
tc.research_text.CONTROLSEALS=Giving them purpose
tc.research_page.CONTROLSEALS.1=Golems cannot do anything they are not told to do. For this purpose you have created Control Seals. You can place these circular clay seals against almost any surface you wish. Once you do they will become become ethereal and intangible, but you will still be able to see them as long as you hold a golem, another seal or §5Golemancer's Bell§0.<BR>The bell will be an important tool as you will use it to fine tune the settings and parameters of the command seals.<BR>Since seals are ethereal you can place down another block in the same spot as you placed a seal. 
tc.research_page.CONTROLSEALS.2=Several seals can also occupy the same block space as long as the are located on different faces. This should allow you to keep things quite compact.<BR>You can retrieve a seal by shift and right-clicking on it with the bell.<LINE>Clicking on a seal with the bell will allow you to tweak its parameters. The exact parameters will vary from seal to seal, but most seals will allow you to give them a priority between -5 and +5 (default 0). Tasks created by higher priority seals will be performed first. You will also be able to see a list of required traits
tc.research_page.CONTROLSEALS.3=that a golem will need to have in order to perform tasks created by that seal.<BR>For example, another seal might require a golem to have the §5Deft§0 trait, or perhaps another seal will require that a golem NOT have the §5Clumsy§0 trait.<BR>For a practical example, look at the §5Collect Seal§0. 
#
tc.research_name.MINDBIOTHAUMIC=秘術生體之心
tc.research_text.MINDBIOTHAUMIC=我思故我在
tc.research_page.MINDBIOTHAUMIC.1=如同你的預期，你所製造的發條之心在抽像推理和自主行動的表現乏善可陳。即使嘗試製造更複雜的發條裝置卻成效不彰，於是你轉而研究已確定具有這些能力的東西：人腦。<BR>雖然剛開始你還很猶豫，但很快便克服了恐懼，並開始深入研究秘術生體學：將血肉、機械與魔法融為一體。<BR>研究結果激勵人心，你很快就學會了如何對發條之心注入殘存灰質，從而製造出更多功能的人工思維。
tc.research_page.MINDBIOTHAUMIC.2=Another advantage if this mind is that it will allow a golem to learn. As it completes tasks it will gain experience and rank up. Higher ranks grants a golem additional health, speed and damage.<BR>Golems start at rank 0 and can improve up to rank 10.<BR>Golems will retain their rank if picked up.
#
tc.research_name.BASICTURRET=自動十字弩
tc.research_text.BASICTURRET=簡易防衛
tc.research_page.BASICTURRET.1=你找到一種方法能夠賦予十字弩思維，使其變為一種簡易的自動炮台。<BR>放置好後的自動十字弩會自動朝著射程內的所有敵對生物開火。遺憾的是它有限的思維能力無法讓你為其調整攻擊目標。<BR>其內部存儲空間也非常有限，但若你願意，你可以將其放置在一個面朝上的發射器上，它就可以自動從發射器中裝填彈藥。<BR>持法杖點擊可以回收它。
#
tc.research_name.ADVANCEDTURRET=Advanced Automated Crossbow
tc.research_text.ADVANCEDTURRET=Not so simple defenses
tc.research_page.ADVANCEDTURRET.1=The Advanced Automated Crossbow works much like its basic couterpart, with a few significant exceptions.<BR>The addition of iron plating makes it much sturdier, and a more complicated loading mechanism gives it a greater rate of fire.<BR>Lastly it is possible to specify the type of targets it can attack.
#
tc.research_name.FOCUSTURRET=自動施術裝置
tc.research_text.FOCUSTURRET=自動核心
tc.research_page.FOCUSTURRET.1=基於你對進階人工思維的研究以及奧術鑽探機的開發，你找到一個方法可以製作出使用法杖核心的自動魔法炮台。<BR>它擁有一個內建的小型魔力庫存，並且能自靈氣中補充魔力。但機器畢竟並非秘術使，它充能的速度較慢，且缺乏機制來減輕發動法杖核心時的魔力消耗。<BR>自動施術裝置能夠放置在任何表面上，並能詳細調整其攻擊的目標。持法杖點擊可以回收它。
#
tc.research_name.SEALCOLLECT=Control Seal: Collect
tc.research_text.SEALCOLLECT=Picking up what you are putting down
tc.research_page.SEALCOLLECT.1=This seal will constantly check an area you define for dropped items. If items are found it will instruct any nearby golems to pick up those items.<BR>You can define the exact dimensions of the area as well as filter out certain items using a white- or blacklist.
tc.research_page.SEALCOLLECT.2=You can now also craft an advanced version of the seal that will allow you to filter more items at once and give you greater control over how the items are filtered, though golems need to be much smarter to perform tasks created by this seal.<BR>You can choose to have the seal ignore NBT or damage values when filtering items, use the ore dictionary, or to have it filter items from the same mod as those in the filter.  
#
tc.research_name.SEALSTORE=Control Seal: Store
tc.research_text.SEALSTORE=Putting away your mess
tc.research_page.SEALSTORE.1=This seal needs to be placed on the side of a container. It will designate the container as a possible destination for any items that golems nearby happen to be holding. As long as the container can accept it, the golems will deliver the item.<BR>You can filter out certain items using a white- or blacklist.
tc.research_page.SEALSTORE.2=You can now also craft an advanced version of the seal that will allow you to filter more items at once and give you greater control over how the items are filtered, though golems need to be much smarter to perform tasks created by this seal.<BR>You can choose to have the seal ignore NBT or damage values when filtering items, use the ore dictionary, or to have it filter items from the same mod as those in the filter.
#
tc.research_name.SEALEMPTY=Control Seal: Empty
tc.research_text.SEALEMPTY=Making a whole new mess
tc.research_page.SEALEMPTY.1=This seal is effectively the opposite of the Store seal. It will empty items from the inventory it is attached to. Any nearby golems will simply take the items and hold. You will need to use other seals to give them instructions as to what they need to do with the items they have taken.<BR>You can filter a specific item to remove or to exclude from removal.  
tc.research_page.SEALEMPTY.2=You can now also craft an advanced version of the seal that will allow you to filter more items at once and give you greater control over how the items are filtered, though golems need to be much smarter to perform tasks created by this seal.<BR>You can choose to have the seal ignore NBT or damage values when filtering items, use the ore dictionary, or to have it filter items from the same mod as those in the filter.<BR>You can also have the seal only check for a single item in the filter at a time in the order they are listed.
#
tc.research_name.SEALPROVIDE=Control Seal: Provide
tc.research_text.SEALPROVIDE=Getting what is needed
tc.research_page.SEALPROVIDE.1=This seal is similar to the Empty seal, except it will only remove an item from the inventory if there is a specific need for it.<BR>Certain seals may request provisioning. If they require specific items for their tasks a secondary task will be created telling a nearby golem to retrieve those items from any inventories marked with a Provide seal.<BR>This task will use the requesting seals priority and the golem needs to meet the requirements for both the Provider seal and the requesting seal.
tc.research_page.SEALPROVIDE.2=The filter on the Provide seal is merely used to compare what items may be taken from the container. The filters (if any) on the requesting seal will determine the exact item taken.
#
tc.research_name.SEALHARVEST=Control Seal: Harvest
tc.research_text.SEALHARVEST=Green mechanical thumbs
tc.research_page.SEALHARVEST.1=This seal will search the designated area for any fully grown crops or other harvestable plants. Once found a golem will be dispatched to harvest the plant.<BR>If required the seal will also attempt to replant the harvested crop as long as seeds (or similar items) are available. 
#
tc.research_name.SEALGUARD=Control Seal: Guard
tc.research_text.SEALGUARD=Protect and Serve
tc.research_page.SEALGUARD.1=When placed this seal will protect and area from intrusion. Any hostile creatures it detects will be targeted by nearby combat-capable golems and attacked.<BR>If the golem has the §5Deft§0 property, any creatures slain will drop experience orbs.<BR>§9This research also unlocks additional golem parts§0. 
tc.research_page.SEALGUARD.2=You can now create an advanced version of the seal that will give you greater control over which creatures your golems will target.
#
tc.research_name.SEALBUTCHER=Control Seal: Butcher
tc.research_text.SEALBUTCHER=Gory to the armpits
tc.research_page.SEALBUTCHER.1=While §5Guard§0 seals can be used to kill animals, they are not very selective.<BR>The butcher seals works much like a §5Guard§0 seal, except it only targets adult animals. Furthermore it will always make sure that at least a breeding pair of animals remain alive. 
#
tc.research_name.SEALBREAK=Control Seal: Block Breaker
tc.research_text.SEALBREAK=*Tap* *Tap* *Tap*
tc.research_page.SEALBREAK.1=This seal commands golems to break any blocks they find in the area.<BR>The hardness of a block does determine how quickly it can be broken.<BR>You can filter what type of blocks are to be broken (or ignored).<BR>It should be noted that due to factors like golem mobility, limited area and speed this seal probably will not make a very effective mining tool, though it could be used as such in a pinch. 
#
tc.research_name.SEALLUMBER=Control Seal: Lumberjack
tc.research_text.SEALLUMBER=And I'm ok
tc.research_page.SEALLUMBER.1=A refinement of the §5Block Breaker§0 seal, the Lumberjack seal will only target wooden logs, but instead of breaking the log the golem is hitting, it will instead break the furthest connected log.<BR>This means that it is highly effective when used to harvest trees as it will effectively chop them from the top down.
#
tc.research_name.SEALUSE=Control Seal: Use
tc.research_text.SEALUSE=Clicky click
tc.research_page.SEALUSE.1=This seal allows a golem to act like a player and left or right click on the block that you have marked.<BR>It can also click with any items it happens to be holding or specific items you have filtered.<BR>The seal will remain even if the block you placed it on is removed, allowing the seal to target empty air if you wish.<BR>If a whitelist items is specified you can also request it to be provisioned.
#
tc.research_name.GOLEMVISION=Golem Biothaumic Eyes
tc.research_text.GOLEMVISION=Improved visual range 
tc.research_page.GOLEMVISION.1=By merging flesh and arcane construct you have crafted a set of highly acute eyes.<BR>Any golem equipped with such a set of peepers will be able to operate at twice the normal range (32 blocks).<BR>§9This research unlocks additional golem parts§0. 
#
tc.research_name.GOLEMCLIMBER=Golem Mobility: Climbing
tc.research_text.GOLEMCLIMBER=There aint no mountains high enough
tc.research_page.GOLEMCLIMBER.1=By equipping a golem with crampons, hooks and various other tools, it will be able to scale sheer walls and other obstacles.<BR>§9This research unlocks additional golem parts§0.
#
tc.research_name.GOLEMFLYER=Golem Mobility: Flight
tc.research_text.GOLEMFLYER=Up, Up and Away!
tc.research_page.GOLEMFLYER.1=By basically chopping off a golems legs and glueing an Arcane levitator in their place you have managed to get a golem to fly. This grants it good (if slightly erratic) mobility, though it does move slower.<BR>§9This research unlocks additional golem parts§0.
#
tc.research_name.GOLEMBREAKER=Golem Manipulation: Block Breaking  
tc.research_text.GOLEMBREAKER=Smash and grab
tc.research_page.GOLEMBREAKER.1=By replacing a golems arms with a set of powerful, diamond tipped pneumatic grinders it will be able to break through all be the hardest material.<BR>§9This research unlocks additional golem parts§0.
#
tc.research_name.GOLEMCOMBATADV=Improved Golem Combat
tc.research_text.GOLEMCOMBATADV=Better Faster Stronger
tc.research_page.GOLEMCOMBATADV.1=You can now craft specialized golem weaponry and armor to make them much more effective in combat.<BR>§9This research unlocks additional golem parts§0.
#
